data.description: Wow!!  Take a look at this STUNNING home on an upgraded lot.  This all-brick home is move-in ready and has lots of upgrades.  The interior finishes are fabulous!  Wall of windows in the Living Room allow for lots of natural lighting.  Beautiful Kitchen opens up to the Living Room and has granite countertops, decorative backsplash and upgraded lighting. Wood vinyl plank flooring throughout, except bedrooms.  The front bedroom may also be used as an office.  It has a closet and French doors.  The roomy Primary Suite has attached Ensuite with beautiful tile work around the large soaking tub, double sinks and separate shower.  Both baths have granite countertops.  And, let's not forget the incredible covered back porch.  You'll definitely want to spend your afternoons here.  Owner has spent thousands in concrete for additional driveway and porch space that will house any RV, boat or recreational vehicle.  Storage building will also remain.  Low tax rate of 1.4873%!!
